&lt;div class="section" id="test-it"&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;test it&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use &lt;a class="reference external" href="<reference refuri="https://tox.readthedocs.org">https://tox.readthedocs.org</reference>"&gt;tox&lt;/a&gt; to run our test suite. After installing &lt;em&gt;tox&lt;/em&gt; you can execute the tests by running &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;tox&lt;/tt&gt; in the project's root directory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The test cases can be found in &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;html5css3/tests.py&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
